      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "One person came up with the scout being a volks-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "wagen, you know how they have to make jokes. But",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "we were treated very nice and in respect, - one",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "person said to Ingrid, you have something there, -",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "meaning the films -",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "\"I could see that they had much knowledge, but",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
