      "text": "could not give themselves away. They did not rid-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "icule us, nor the films, nor the whole UFO idea. I",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "did not go to NASA to convince them, but to cons-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "ult them.\"",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "He added:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "\"This meeting with NASA was a different matter",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
