    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "On March 20th, Fred sent me a photostat letter",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "from the UFO spokesman at the Pentagon in Wa-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "shington D.C. (see back pages)",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "\"DEPARTMENT OF THE AIR FORCE",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "Washington 20330",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "Office Of The Secretary",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "Mar 17 1967",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "Dear Mr. Steckling:",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "Your letter concerning your unidentified flying",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "object (UFO) film finally reached my office - - -",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "Office of Information for Project Blue Book, the Air",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "Force UFO program.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "The Air Force would be very interested in review-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "ing your film. If you would get in touch with me at",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "the Pentagon, we will arrange a showing for any",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "Monday which is convenient for you. My number is",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "0 - - - - or 0 - - - -.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "Thank you for offering to show your film; I am",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "looking forward to hearing from you.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "Sincerely",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
