      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "text": "Fred wrote of the visit:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "text": "\"Our Pentagon visit was Monday March 20th at",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "2 p.m. at Colonel Freeman's office. - Madeleine",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "text": "came along - Several high commission officers rev-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "text": "iewed the Sept. 7th film three times, and Colonel",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "text": "Freeman stated: \"This is the best film I've seen yet.\"",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 67,
      "text": "and \"I have never seen anything like this before.\"",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68,
      "text": "He told me to inform the UFO investigation comm-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 69,
      "text": "ittee in Colorado - (- the new University of Colorado",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 71,
      "text": "UFO investigation study, - R.C.) - and them",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 72,
      "text": "some pictures.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 73,
      "text": "\"Madeleine's and G.A.'s films were already known",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 74,
      "text": "to them - from T.V. - and no comment was made on",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 75,
      "text": "them. They seemed to know all three of us - Ingrid",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 76,
      "text": "was there - they gave this impression.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 77,
      "text": "\"The Colonel said: \"What about the scoutships",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 78,
      "text": "we are supposed to have in Dayton?\" so we ans-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 79,
      "text": "wered, \"What about and how about it?\" They did",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 80,
      "text": "not confirm anything or otherwise. But here too we",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 81,
      "text": "were treated respectfully, and returned the same to",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 82,
      "text": "them -.\"",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 83,
