      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 84,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 85,
      "text": "Later, I received a fuller description of events.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 86,
      "text": "\"When I took the film September 7th, we were",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 87,
      "text": "between Mannheim and Frankfurt traveling North. The",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 88,
      "text": "time was about 11.45 a.m., no clouds, about seventy",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89,
      "text": "degrees, Fahrenheit. Although power-lines and trees",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 90,
      "text": "were flying by, while I took the film, if there was a",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 91,
      "text": "station it surely swished by so fast that it was imp-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 92,
      "text": "ossible to make out any signs, etc. In this case you",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 93,
      "text": "have to take my word for it. I was already before",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 94,
      "text": "alerted of the Brothers before the film, and became",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 95,
      "text": "aware of a group of 10 to 12 cigarette shaped",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 96,
      "text": "objects high in the sky (12 o'clock up.) I jumped",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 97,
      "text": "back to grab the camera, a 8 mm Revere, 30 mm",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 98,
      "text": "powerzoom, Chicago build and opened the window",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 99,
      "text": "all the way to eliminate any reflections and started",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 100,
      "text": "filming. All in all, 6 groups of ten to twelve space-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 101,
      "text": "craft appeared one after another and moved along",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 102,
      "text": "the sky like Dolphins in the water, as an example.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 103,
      "text": "Appearing and disappearing, the armada traveled to",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 104,
      "text": "about 9 o'clock (position) and disappeared complet-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 105,
      "text": "ely, giving me the privilege to take about 23 feet of",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 106,
      "text": "Kodak color film.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 107,
      "text": "\"There were quite some people on the train, some",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 108,
      "text": "of them looking out of their windows, becoming",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 109,
      "text": "aware of the objects. As we could see they all had",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 110,
      "text": "big question-marks on their faces. They had never",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 111,
      "text": "seen anything like this before. I might add, there",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 112,
      "text": "was no fear on their faces. Ingrid and myself also",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 113,
      "text": "Glenn, we could hardly believe it, ever to be pres-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 114,
      "text": "ented with such an opportunity of taking that many",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 115,
      "text": "ships on film and all at once. We stood on the win-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 116,
      "text": "dow, Ingrid saying only, \"oh, my God\" and our every",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 117,
      "text": "hair was standing up at this wonderful sight. We will",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 118,
      "text": "never forget this experience and are surely grateful",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 119,
      "text": "for it. -\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 120,
      "text": "UNQUOTE.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 121,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 122,
      "text": "I wrote to Fred, asking him if I could use his pict-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 123,
      "text": "ures and correspondence in UFO CONTACT. He",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124,
      "text": "wrote back:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 125,
      "text": "\"You can go ahead and use what you feel is right",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 126,
      "text": "concerning my visit to NASA and the pictures -",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 127,
      "text": "\"As you know, my work in this cause has no conn-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128,
      "text": "ections in pleasing my Ego, and therefore it does",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129,
      "text": "not matter to me if my name is used or not. Import-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 130,
      "text": "ant is the work, not us. -",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 131,
      "text": "\"We all know George Adamski has given much to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
